		<content:encoded><![CDATA[I just found a better template library than the one we use (that came with PHPBB): <a href="http://smarty.php.net/">Smarty</a>. It's more powerful, caches templates and is written by one of the PHP guys. Although it's <a href="http://www.phpinsider.com/benchmarks/">not the fastest</a> template engine for simple things, but seems to be fast when you can offload the work to the template.]]></content:encoded>
